data.description: This Expansive Home with pretty views, 17.18 acres, equestrian barns has everything you need to enjoy Mountain living, with a convenient location 30 min from Asheville. On the main level, walk into the large open floor plan, where the Virginia Fieldstone Fireplace reaches up 2 stories and creates the center piece of this expansive living area. The hills above and the horses in the pasture below create a pretty scene from where you will sit in your kitchen, dining room, or on the wrap around porch. Upper level has 2 bdrms with walk-in closets and large open area for an office or sitting area. Main level has 3 bedrooms with a large shared bathroom. Downstairs has a large garage and large living area for a game room, art studio and more. Laundry is downstairs through the garage. Plenty of parking downstairs and on the main level behind the house. Equestrian barn with tack room and tractor garage in the pasture both have electric. A second well for the horses as well as a spring fed pond.
